    {# Water & Sewer #}
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Water &amp; Sewer Bill</h2>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl p-5 mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-800">
          <strong>Important:</strong> Payments made on the due date must be completed before 5:00 PM to avoid interest and penalty. Payments made after 5 PM will be applied as the next business day's transaction.
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Your account must be settled by 5:00 PM on the day <strong>before</strong> the service turn-off date or your water service will be interrupted. A <strong>$50.00 service fee</strong> for residential customers and <strong>$100.00 service fee</strong> for commercial customers will be applied to your outstanding bill.
      </p>
      <a href="https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/finance/pages/online-payments-0" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gov-blue text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-gov-blue-dark transition-colors duration-200 text-sm">
