        Pay Water &amp; Sewer Bill
      </a>
    </div>

    {# Property Tax #}
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Property Taxes</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Property Tax Bills must be paid in the <strong>full amount due</strong>, including any interest and penalty. Bills are assessed and mailed on July 1 of each year. The City's current tax rate is <strong>$0.625 per $100 of assessed value</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Real properties located within the City limits are subject to taxation unless specifically exempted. Each property is reassessed every three years by the State Department of Assessments and Taxation.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/finance/pages/online-payments-0" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gov-blue text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-gov-blue-dark transition-colors duration-200 text-sm">
          Pay Property Tax
        </a>
        <a href="/services/taxes/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-slate-300 text-slate-700 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:border-gov-blue hover:text-gov-blue transition-colors duration-200 text-sm">
          Tax Information
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

